                                                                                                                                    subject that has been granted access to informaon can grant its privileges to other
                                                                                                                                    subjects;

                                                                                                              AC-03(04)(c)          <AC-03(04)_ODP[01] discreonary access control policy> and <AC-03(04)_ODP[02]
                                                                                                                                    discreonary access control policy> are enforced where the policy speciﬁes that a
                                                                                                                                    subject that has been granted access to informaon can change security aributes
                                                                                                                                    on subjects, objects, the system, or the system’s components;

                                                                                                              AC-03(04)(d)          <AC-03(04)_ODP[01] discreonary access control policy> and <AC-03(04)_ODP[02]
                                                                                                                                    discreonary access control policy> are enforced where the policy speciﬁes that
                                                                                                                                    a subject that has been granted access to informaon can choose the security
                                                                                                                                    aributes to be associated with newly created or revised objects;

                                                                                                              AC-03(04)(e)          <AC-03(04)_ODP[01] discreonary access control policy> and <AC-03(04)_ODP[02]
                                                                                                                                    discreonary access control policy> are enforced where the policy speciﬁes that a
                                                                                                                                    subject that has been granted access to informaon can change the rules governing
                                                                                                                                    access control.

